<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$xiahao" href="/people/xiahao">夏昊Film</a>，<strong title="公路车电影摄影发烧友／篮球足球爱好者／法语西语初学者" class="zu-question-my-bio">公路车电影摄影发烧友／篮球足球爱好者／…</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="2">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$michael-39-45" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/michael-39-45" class="zg-link" title="Michael">Michael</a></span>
</span>


<span>赞同</span>


